Internal view of posterior part 
<emphasis id="93B3926B229DC91B6A54C33BEAA3234E" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="13">g, h</emphasis>
paratype male adult: 
<emphasis id="AFEA7A1C1D30BD51916BFF21D1C5A7E3" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="13">g</emphasis>
